<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.1.1">
<l>kaiyār cakkaratteṅkaru māṇikkamē yeṉṟeṉṟu</l>
<l>poyyē kaimmaicollippuṟamēpuṟa mēyāṭi</l>
<l>meyyē peṟṟoḻintēṉ vitivāykkiṉṟu kāppārā</l>
<l>raiyō kaṇṇapirā ṉaṟaiyō viṉippōṉālē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying [and] saying “my black ruby with the discuss of which [his] hand is full”,</l>
<l>speaking but lie [and] ignominy, dancing outside, outside,</l>
<l>I ended up obtaining the truth. Fate prevails. Who will guard [against it]?</l>
<l>Ayyo, if lord Kṛṣṇa goes now, [will it be] a blow?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
